<div class="about-wrapper">
    <div class="about-content">
        <p class="dropcap">Hello, I'm David. I like to take photographs in my free time. I try to spend as much time outside as possible, hence its mostly landscape photographs. 
            I work as a DevOps Engineer and I find being outside, shooting, to be a great way to balance things. 
            The photographs on this site were taken with a variety of cameras, most of them analog. Using less CPU-time in your life is nice.</p>
        <p>All most all of my photographs are taken around Switzerland. A few are from Scandinavia or further away (From me at least :P). 
             This site serves two purposes. Firstly, it is meant as a replacement for my old Instagram account, which I do not maintain anymore.
            I have better ways to spend my time, than doomscrolling through that misbegotten app. The second use is as a sort of photographic diary for myself to have my favorite shots in one place.
            There are dedicated tools for this, but I don't care. I will add some metadata to my photographs in the future, but for now you can just enjoy the images as they are. Done is better than perfect.</p>
            
